consent.using-this-app: Adiga oo adeegsanaya barnaamijkan abka ah, waxaad xaqiijineysaa inaad kaliya galeyso macluumaadkaaga ama laguu oggolaaday inaad geliso macluumaadka adiga oo matalaya dadka kale.
consent.any-data-stored: Macluumaad kasta oo aad galiso barnaamijkan waxaa lagu keydiyaa gudaha aaladdaada loomana gudbinayo abuuraha barnaamijkan ama cid kale. Xogta falanqaynta aan la aqoon ee ku saabsan adeegsiga barnaamijka ayaa laga yaabaa in lala socdo loona wareejiyo abuuraha abkan.
consent.more-information: Macluumaad dheeraad ah oo ku saabsan sida aan u xafidanno xogta una hubinno in asturnaanta la heli karo {halkan}.
consent.medical-disclaimer: Isticmaalka barnaamijkan waa inaan loo aqoonsan inuu yahay la-talin caafimaad oo uusan beddel u ahayn dhakhtar ama xirfadle daryeel caafimaad kale. Dhammaan cadaadiska dhiigga iyo sumadaha sonkorta dhiigga, sida "sare", "dhexdhexaad", ama "hooseeya", waxay la jaan qaadayaan tallaabooyinka guud ee la aqbalay ee calaamadeynta cadaadiska dhiigga iyo sonkorta dhiigga loomana siiyo talo caafimaad oo gaar ah shaqsiyaadka. Fadlan la tasho dhakhtarkaaga inta ama ka hor intaadan adeegsan barnaamijkan.
